Joyous celebration dies in an accident&nbsp; Joyous Celebration is a South African Gospel choir which was formed in 1994 following the success of South Africa's first democratic elections. Joyous celebration tour bus crashed on their way back home from performing at an event . The accident happened at 3am this morning. Everyone in the bus was sleeping as they were all tired. The driver then fell asleep too and that's what led the bus from getting off the road into the bushes where it hit a huge rock and rolled two times 10 died while the others are critical in hospital with severe injuries. Source:viral-spy.blogspot.co.ke